											<h1 itemprop="headline">IPL 2025, PBKS vs DC updates: Punjab Kings v Delhi Capitals abandoned in Dharamsala as players, fans evacuated from HPCA Stadium</h1>
											<h2 itemprop="description" class="synopsis">IPL 2025, PBKS vs DC Match abandoned: The game had started after a lengthy delay due to rain in Dharamsala. Then after 10.1 overs, the PBKS vs DC game was abandoned with fans and players evacuated out of the HPCA Stadium. </h2>
											<div class="ie-authorbox">
						<div class="editorbx fleft editor-details-new-change">
