Read the full statement from BCCI&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>IPL Suspended for One Week</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>The Board of Control for Cricket in India has suspended the ongoing season of the Indian Premier League (IPL 2025) for one week."Further updates regarding the new schedule and venues of the tournament will be announced in due course after a comprehensive assessment of the situation in consultation with relevant authorities and stakeholders," said BCCI secretary Devajit Saikia in a stement.&nbsp;</p>

<p><a href="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/ipl/ipl-suspended-for-one-week-bcci-full-statement-india-9992783/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em><strong>Read the full statement from BCCI&nbsp;</strong></em></a></p></div>
