</figure>
<p><br /><br /><br /></p>
<figure class="image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://indianexpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AP25128588722547.jpg" alt="" ><br />
<figcaption>Workers leave the ground after the authorities asked to evacuate the stadium during the Indian Premier League cricket match between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals at Himachal Pradesh Cricket Association Stadium in Dharamshala, India, Thursday, May 8, 2025. (AP Photo)</figcaption>
</figure>
<p><br /><br /></p>
<figure class="image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://indianexpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/AP25128590418885.jpg" alt="" ><br />
<figcaption>Spectators leave the stands after the authorities asked to evacuate the stadium during the Indian Premier League cricket match between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals at Himachal Pradesh Cricket Association Stadium in Dharamshala, India, Thursday, May 8, 2025. (AP Photo)</figcaption>
</figure></div>
