<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508212928" data-timeframe="20250508212928"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011796"><div class="And after an abrupt stoppage in the PBKS vs DC game, we have news that the match has been abandoned!&amp;nbsp;\nInitially, it looked like a floodlights malfunction. But then, even as the official broadcasters tried to blame a &quot;significant technical failure at the HPCA Stadium&quot;, Arun Dhumal, IPL Chairman told news agency IANS that the PBKS vs DC match was &quot;called off as a precautionary measure, based on the red alert issued in Jammu&quot;.&amp;nbsp;\nMedia reports said that fans in the HPCA Stadiunm were being evacuated from the stadium.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\n\n\n\n&lt;img src=&quot;https:\/\/indianexpress.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/New-Project-2025-05-08T213925.693.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; \/&gt;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
