							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T22:04:49+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: MATCH ABANDONED!">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="And after an abrupt stoppage in the PBKS vs DC game, we have news that the match has been abandoned!&nbsp;
Initially, it looked like a floodlights malfunction. But then, even as the official broadcasters tried to blame a "significant technical failure at the HPCA Stadium", Arun Dhumal, IPL Chairman told news agency IANS that the PBKS vs DC match was "called off as a precautionary measure, based on the red alert issued in Jammu".&nbsp;
Media reports said that fans in the HPCA Stadiunm were being evacuated from the stadium.&nbsp;&nbsp;



">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: MATCH ABANDONED!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p><em><strong>And after an abrupt stoppage in the PBKS vs DC game, we have news that the match has been abandoned!&nbsp;</strong></em></p>
<p>Initially, it looked like a floodlights malfunction. But then, even as the official broadcasters tried to blame a "significant technical failure at the HPCA Stadium", Arun Dhumal, IPL Chairman told news agency IANS that the <em><strong>PBKS vs DC match was "called off as a precautionary measure, based on the red alert issued in Jammu".&nbsp;</strong></em></p>
<p>Media reports said that fans in the HPCA Stadiunm were being evacuated from the stadium.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p><img loading="lazy"  src="https://indianexpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/New-Project-2025-05-08T213925.693.jpg" alt="" ></p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
