							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Priyansh Arya has a bit of a tired swing at the first ball of Natarajan's first ball of the 11th over and the ball flies into the grateful palms of Madhav Tiwari! And we finally have a wicket! The ball seems to hit the batter's helmet after a top edge. If that had not hit the helmet, maybe it would have landed in a safe area and gone for a four.

Priyansh Arya c Tiwari b Natarajan 70 (34b 5x4 6x6) SR: 205.88">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: GONE!!!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Priyansh Arya has a bit of a tired swing at the first ball of Natarajan's first ball of the 11th over and the ball flies into the grateful palms of Madhav Tiwari! And we finally have a wicket! The ball seems to hit the batter's helmet after a top edge. If that had not hit the helmet, maybe it would have landed in a safe area and gone for a four.</p>

<p><em><strong>Priyansh Arya c Tiwari b Natarajan 70 (34b 5x4 6x6) SR: 205.88</strong></em></p></div>
