<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508212348" data-timeframe="20250508212348"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011794"><div class="First ball of the 10th over from Kuldeep Yadav is hit for a 96-metre six from Priyansh Arya that's landed on the roof. And we have a change of ball here.\nThe change of ball doesn't help much. Not change in fortunes for Kuldeep as the second ball is also tonked for a six over the head of the bowler. After a quiet third ball, Arya hits a four on the fourth ball.&amp;nbsp;\n16 runs off the first four balls. And now Prabhsimran Singh sinks to his knees, he seems to be battling some cramps. So we have a hold up. And as we restart, Prabhsimran Singh gets to his 50 off just 28 balls!&amp;nbsp;\nAs the over ends, Punjab Kings are 122\/0. And we are just at the halfway mark of the first innings!" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
