							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T21:23:48+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: BOOOM!">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="First ball of the 10th over from Kuldeep Yadav is hit for a 96-metre six from Priyansh Arya that's landed on the roof. And we have a change of ball here.
The change of ball doesn't help much. Not change in fortunes for Kuldeep as the second ball is also tonked for a six over the head of the bowler. After a quiet third ball, Arya hits a four on the fourth ball.&nbsp;
16 runs off the first four balls. And now Prabhsimran Singh sinks to his knees, he seems to be battling some cramps. So we have a hold up. And as we restart, Prabhsimran Singh gets to his 50 off just 28 balls!&nbsp;
As the over ends, Punjab Kings are 122/0. And we are just at the halfway mark of the first innings!">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: BOOOM!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>First ball of the 10th over from Kuldeep Yadav is hit for a 96-metre six from Priyansh Arya that's landed on the roof. And we have a change of ball here.</p>
<p>The change of ball doesn't help much. Not change in fortunes for Kuldeep as the second ball is also tonked for a six over the head of the bowler. After a quiet third ball, Arya hits a four on the fourth ball.&nbsp;</p>
<p>16 runs off the first four balls. And now Prabhsimran Singh sinks to his knees, he seems to be battling some cramps. So we have a hold up. And as we restart, P<em><strong>rabhsimran Singh gets to his 50 off just 28 balls!&nbsp;</strong></em></p>
<p><em><strong>As the over ends, Punjab Kings are 122/0. And we are just at the halfway mark of the first innings!</strong></em></p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
