							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Desperate for a breakthrough, Delhi hand the ball to young debutant Madhav Tiwari the ball. And he's hit for 14 runs in his first over in the IPL. This includes two back-to-back fours from Prabhsimran Singh.&nbsp;
And we have the Punjab opening batters reaching the 100-rum partnership.&nbsp;101 runs off 55 balls for the Punjab openers today!&nbsp;&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 9 overs, Punjab Kings are 103/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Desperate for a breakthrough, Delhi hand the ball to young debutant Madhav Tiwari the ball. And he's hit for 14 runs in his first over in the IPL. This includes two back-to-back fours from Prabhsimran Singh.&nbsp;</p>
<p>And we have the Punjab opening batters reaching the 100-rum partnership.&nbsp;101 runs off 55 balls for the Punjab openers today!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>
