<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508211428" data-timeframe="20250508211428"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011792"><div class="Kuldeep Yadav comes in. And ends up giving away 10 runs in that over. The highlight of the over was a reverse hit from Priyansh Arya over backward point. That shot came right when Kuldeep and Delhi would have felt that the over was goign very well for them: Kuldeep, after all, had given away just 6 runs off the first four balls. And then, on the fifth ball came the reverse hit slapped to the boundary.&amp;nbsp;\n10 runs off that over.&amp;nbsp;\nRicky Ponting, talking to the broadcasters, calls Priyansh Arya as 'one of the finds of the tournament'.&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
