							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T21:15:17+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 8 overs, Punjab Kings are 89/0">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Kuldeep Yadav comes in. And ends up giving away 10 runs in that over. The highlight of the over was a reverse hit from Priyansh Arya over backward point. That shot came right when Kuldeep and Delhi would have felt that the over was goign very well for them: Kuldeep, after all, had given away just 6 runs off the first four balls. And then, on the fifth ball came the reverse hit slapped to the boundary.&nbsp;
10 runs off that over.&nbsp;
Ricky Ponting, talking to the broadcasters, calls Priyansh Arya as 'one of the finds of the tournament'.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 8 overs, Punjab Kings are 89/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Kuldeep Yadav comes in. And ends up giving away 10 runs in that over. The highlight of the over was a reverse hit from Priyansh Arya over backward point. That shot came right when Kuldeep and Delhi would have felt that the over was goign very well for them: Kuldeep, after all, had given away just 6 runs off the first four balls. And then, on the fifth ball came the reverse hit slapped to the boundary.&nbsp;</p>
<p>10 runs off that over.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Ricky Ponting, talking to the broadcasters, calls Priyansh Arya as 'one of the finds of the tournament'.&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
