<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508210903" data-timeframe="20250508210903"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011791"><div class="Axar Patel is back to bowl another over and Priyansh Arya tonks the fourth ball of his over for a maximum over the long off boundary. The Delhi Capitals fielder tried his best to grab the ball, but it was a bit much even for him.&amp;nbsp;\nOn the next ball, Priyansh Arya works the ball on the leg side to run a single. Priyansh Arya reaches his half century off just 25 balls, thanks to 4 fours and 4 sixes.&amp;nbsp;In his debut IPL season, Priyansh Arya already has his second half century in the IPL. He also has a hundred this season!&amp;nbsp;\n&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
