							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T21:09:03+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: 50 for Priyansh Arya">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Axar Patel is back to bowl another over and Priyansh Arya tonks the fourth ball of his over for a maximum over the long off boundary. The Delhi Capitals fielder tried his best to grab the ball, but it was a bit much even for him.&nbsp;
On the next ball, Priyansh Arya works the ball on the leg side to run a single. Priyansh Arya reaches his half century off just 25 balls, thanks to 4 fours and 4 sixes.&nbsp;In his debut IPL season, Priyansh Arya already has his second half century in the IPL. He also has a hundred this season!&nbsp;
&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: 50 for Priyansh Arya</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Axar Patel is back to bowl another over and Priyansh Arya tonks the fourth ball of his over for a maximum over the long off boundary. The Delhi Capitals fielder tried his best to grab the ball, but it was a bit much even for him.&nbsp;</p>
<p>On the next ball, Priyansh Arya works the ball on the leg side to run a single. <em><strong>Priyansh Arya reaches his half century off just 25 balls, thanks to 4 fours and 4 sixes.&nbsp;</strong><strong>In his debut IPL season, Priyansh Arya already has his second half century in the IPL. He also has a hundred this season!&nbsp;</strong></em></p>
<p><em><strong>&nbsp;</strong></em></p></div>
							</div>
