							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Delhi Capitals hand the ball to T Natarajan, who gets to bowl for the first time this IPL season. And he makes an instant impact! He beats Arya with swing twice in the second and third balls of his over. Just four runs in that over!&nbsp;
So Punjab Kings reach 69/0 after the powerplay ends.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 6 overs, Punjab Kings are 69/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Delhi Capitals hand the ball to T Natarajan, who gets to bowl for the first time this IPL season. And he makes an instant impact! He beats Arya with swing twice in the second and third balls of his over. Just four runs in that over!&nbsp;</p>
<p>So Punjab Kings reach 69/0 after the powerplay ends.&nbsp;</p></div>
