							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="So Axar Patel replaces Starc and is tonked for 15 runs! That includes a six off the final ball from Priyansh Arya right after he misses the fifth ball completely and gets lucky not to see his stumps rattled. Axar strayed on the pads, and was tonked!&nbsp;
There was also a boundary and the batters running for three runs on another ball.&nbsp;
15 runs coming off that first over from Axar Patel!&nbsp;&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 5 overs, Punjab Kings are 65/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>So Axar Patel replaces Starc and is tonked for 15 runs! That includes a six off the final ball from Priyansh Arya right after he misses the fifth ball completely and gets lucky not to see his stumps rattled. Axar strayed on the pads, and was tonked!&nbsp;</p>
<p>There was also a boundary and the batters running for three runs on another ball.&nbsp;</p>
<p>15 runs coming off that first over from Axar Patel!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>
