						<div>
							<time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2025-05-08T20:55:03+05:30"></time>
							<time itemprop="url" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/#tie-lb-20250508205503"></time>
							<span itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="author" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
								<meta content="amitkamath" itemprop="name">
							</span>
							<span itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="image">
								<meta itemprop="url" content="https://images.indianexpress.com/2025/05/PBKS-VS-DC-EVACUATION.jpg">
								<meta content="480" itemprop="width">
								<meta content="267" itemprop="height">
							</span>
							<span itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="publisher">
								<span itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="logo">
									<meta content="https://images.indianexpress.com/2019/11/ienewlogo3_new.png" itemprop="url">
									<meta content="125" itemprop="width">
									<meta content="26" itemprop="height">
								</span>
								<meta content="The Indian Express" itemprop="name">
							</span>
							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T20:55:03+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 4 overs, Punjab Kings are 50/0">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="50 runs up for Punjab in just four overs! Two sixes and a four from Priyansh Arya in that over off Chameera.&nbsp;
Incredible fielding there from Rizvi on the first ball as he dives full length and prevents a certain boundary. Arya smashes the second ball for a 64-metre six on the same side, over Rizvi's head almost!&nbsp;
On the fourth ball, Chameera flummoxes Arya and gets an inside edge. But thankfully for the Punjab batter, the ball clips the inside edge and hits him on the thigh pad to run away to the boundary past the keeper. A healthy serving of luck here for both Punjab batters so far.&nbsp;
And Arya ends that over by tonking the final ball for a maximum!&nbsp;
18 runs coming off that over from Chameera.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After 4 overs, Punjab Kings are 50/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p><em><strong>50 runs up for Punjab in just four overs! Two sixes and a four from Priyansh Arya in that over off Chameera.&nbsp;</strong></em></p>
<p>Incredible fielding there from Rizvi on the first ball as he dives full length and prevents a certain boundary. Arya smashes the second ball for a 64-metre six on the same side, over Rizvi's head almost!&nbsp;</p>
<p>On the fourth ball, Chameera flummoxes Arya and gets an inside edge. But thankfully for the Punjab batter, the ball clips the inside edge and hits him on the thigh pad to run away to the boundary past the keeper. A healthy serving of luck here for both Punjab batters so far.&nbsp;</p>
<p>And Arya ends that over by tonking the final ball for a maximum!&nbsp;</p>
<p><em><strong>18 runs coming off that over from Chameera.&nbsp;</strong></em></p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>
<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508204845" data-timeframe="20250508204845"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011787"><div class="After the first two overs saw Priyansh Arya going for some hits to the fence, we have Prabhsimran Singh taking on Mitchell Starc: he hits the Australian for a boundary on the first ball on the legside, with a casual flick off his pads. Starc responds with a typical fast bowler's reply: a bouncer straight fast his eyeline.&amp;nbsp;\nTwo dot balls after the boundary on the first ball. And then, Singh gets an inside edge while going for a drive on the fourth ball, and the ball flies to the boundary past the stumps! Lucky there for the batter.&amp;nbsp;\nStarc responds to this four with a guided bouncer that Singh just about fends off! Singh responds to that yorker by finally getting a drive right! Three boundaries in that over! And we have 12&amp;nbsp;runs coming off that second over from Starc!&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
							<div class="ieo-datetime">
								<span>20:48 (IST)</span><span>08 May 2025</span></div>
