							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T20:43:33+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After two overs, Punjab Kings are 20/0">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Chameera comes on and beats Priyansh Arya for line on the first ball!&nbsp; Arya responds with a single on the next ball. And after another single on ball three, Arya is back at the crease. On the fourth ball, he's beaten once again!&nbsp;
He responds this time, by walking across the stumps and flicking the ball away to deep backward square leg, where it's kept in bounds by the fielder. And just when we think the over is over, we have a no ball for overstepping.
We would have had just four runs from that over if that no ball wasn't bowled. But Arya hits the free hit ball over the fielders in the circle on the off side for a boundary.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After two overs, Punjab Kings are 20/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Chameera comes on and beats Priyansh Arya for line on the first ball!&nbsp; Arya responds with a single on the next ball. And after another single on ball three, Arya is back at the crease. On the fourth ball, he's beaten once again!&nbsp;</p>
<p>He responds this time, by walking across the stumps and flicking the ball away to deep backward square leg, where it's kept in bounds by the fielder. And just when we think the over is over, we have a no ball for overstepping.</p>
<p>We would have had just four runs from that over if that no ball wasn't bowled. But Arya hits the free hit ball over the fielders in the circle on the off side for a boundary.&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>
<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508203733" data-timeframe="20250508203733"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011785"><div class="First ball on the pads of Priyansh Arya from Starc, gets cut and runs away to the boundary! Second ball, Starc over-corrects and sees the ball hoicked over the top of the in-field on the off side and it races away to the boundary again.&amp;nbsp;\nEight runs off two balls.&amp;nbsp;\nAfter a dot ball on ball 3, Arya cuts the ball and KL Rahul throws himself on the ground at point to save the ball from reaching the ropes. Good fielding from the Delhi star.&amp;nbsp;\nAnd there is some drama on the fifth ball as Prabhsimran Singh pulls out of the ball's line right in time before Starc releases the ball. There is someone walking behind the bowler's arm, which hinders the batter's sight.&amp;nbsp;\nJust three singles off the final three balls, so a good comeback from Starc after being hit for two fours on the first two balls!&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
							<div class="ieo-datetime">
