							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T20:37:33+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After one over, Punjab Kings are 11/0">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="First ball on the pads of Priyansh Arya from Starc, gets cut and runs away to the boundary! Second ball, Starc over-corrects and sees the ball hoicked over the top of the in-field on the off side and it races away to the boundary again.&nbsp;
Eight runs off two balls.&nbsp;
After a dot ball on ball 3, Arya cuts the ball and KL Rahul throws himself on the ground at point to save the ball from reaching the ropes. Good fielding from the Delhi star.&nbsp;
And there is some drama on the fifth ball as Prabhsimran Singh pulls out of the ball's line right in time before Starc releases the ball. There is someone walking behind the bowler's arm, which hinders the batter's sight.&nbsp;
Just three singles off the final three balls, so a good comeback from Starc after being hit for two fours on the first two balls!&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: After one over, Punjab Kings are 11/0</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>First ball on the pads of Priyansh Arya from Starc, gets cut and runs away to the boundary! Second ball, Starc over-corrects and sees the ball hoicked over the top of the in-field on the off side and it races away to the boundary again.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Eight runs off two balls.&nbsp;</p>
<p>After a dot ball on ball 3, Arya cuts the ball and KL Rahul throws himself on the ground at point to save the ball from reaching the ropes. Good fielding from the Delhi star.&nbsp;</p>
<p>And there is some drama on the fifth ball as Prabhsimran Singh pulls out of the ball's line right in time before Starc releases the ball. There is someone walking behind the bowler's arm, which hinders the batter's sight.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Just three singles off the final three balls, so a good comeback from Starc after being hit for two fours on the first two balls!&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
