							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Here we go!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>So finally after the long delay, we are ready for the game between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals.</p>
<p>Starc has the ball for Delhi.</p>
<p>Priyansh Arya, Prabhsimran Singh out in the middle for Punjab, with Priyansh facing ball one!&nbsp;</p>
<p>Here we go!&nbsp;</p></div>
