							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="So the rains have gone away and the umpires have decided after the ground inspection that the toss will happen at 8.15. The game will start at 8.30 pm.&nbsp;And despite the delay, we will have a full 20 overs game!&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: TOSS COMING UP</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>So the rains have gone away and the umpires have decided after the ground inspection that the <em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>t</strong></span><strong>oss will happen at 8.15. The game will start at 8.30 pm.&nbsp;</strong><strong>And despite the delay, we will have a full 20 overs game!&nbsp;</strong></em></p></div>
