							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Closer to game now">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="So we have the usualy pre-match rituals being done in the middle by players from both sides. Delhi Capitals' pacve spearhead, Mitchell Starc, is spotted marking his run up with paint. And Punjab Kings captain Shreyas Iyer is doing his visualising in front of the stumps on the22-yeard strip that is finally visible now after that blue cover is taken off! Kuldeep Yadav is turning his arm at one corner of the ground.&nbsp;
Meanwhile, most of the Delhi players including Faf du Plessis and KL Rahul are playing a game of keey-uppies with the football. It seems like the players who are having too much fun in this pursuit, because the player who drops the ball, gets flicked on the forehead by the others players playing. KL Rahul getting his fair share of forehead flicks from teammates, but he's grinning from ear to ear!&nbsp; &nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Closer to game now</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>So we have the usualy pre-match rituals being done in the middle by players from both sides. Delhi Capitals' pacve spearhead, Mitchell Starc, is spotted marking his run up with paint. And Punjab Kings captain Shreyas Iyer is doing his visualising in front of the stumps on the22-yeard strip that is finally visible now after that blue cover is taken off! Kuldeep Yadav is turning his arm at one corner of the ground.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Meanwhile, most of the Delhi players including Faf du Plessis and KL Rahul are playing a game of keey-uppies with the football. It seems like the players who are having too much fun in this pursuit, because the player who drops the ball, gets flicked on the forehead by the others players playing. KL Rahul getting his fair share of forehead flicks from teammates, but he's grinning from ear to ear!&nbsp; &nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
