							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="We have visuals of the players from both teams -- Delhi Capitals and the Punjab Kings -- warming up with some football in the middle. We are told that a ground inspection will happen at 8 pm. And that will decide how the rest of the evening pans out. For now, the rain is gone. But the skies in Dharamsala are still pregnant with clouds and the threat of rains is still around.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Ground insepction at 8 pm</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>We have visuals of the players from both teams -- Delhi Capitals and the Punjab Kings -- warming up with some football in the middle. We are told that a ground inspection will happen at 8 pm. And that will decide how the rest of the evening pans out. For now, the rain is gone. But the skies in Dharamsala are still pregnant with clouds and the threat of rains is still around.&nbsp;</p></div>
