							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T19:11:10+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Punjab could qualify today">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="A win today for the Punjab Kings could see them became the first team out of the 10 to qualify for the IPL 2025 playoffs. But for that, they need the rain Gods to relent. Right now, it looks very gloomy in Dharamsala.&nbsp;
As former India cricketer Murali Karthik said in the pitch report: 'There's a bit of rain in the air. We have had a bit of a delay even to do the pitch report.'&nbsp;
Just look at the skies behind Marthik when he was doing the pitch report.
">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Punjab could qualify today</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>A win today for the Punjab Kings could see them became the first team out of the 10 to qualify for the IPL 2025 playoffs. But for that, they need the rain Gods to relent. Right now, it looks very gloomy in Dharamsala.&nbsp;</p>
<p>As former India cricketer Murali Karthik said in the pitch report: 'There's a bit of rain in the air. We have had a bit of a delay even to do the pitch report.'&nbsp;</p>
<p>Just look at the skies behind Marthik when he was doing the pitch report.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy"  src="https://indianexpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/MURALI-A-.jpg" alt="" ></p></div>
