<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508190220" data-timeframe="20250508190220"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011773"><div class="The toss at Dharamsala for the game between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals has been delayed due to rain!&amp;nbsp;\nWe have visuals of the 22-yard pitch being covered by a blue covers. And now we await the rain to relent so that the match can begin. The weather in Dharamsala is looking grim and cloudy.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
