							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T19:02:20+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: RAIN DELAYS TOSS!">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="The toss at Dharamsala for the game between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals has been delayed due to rain!&nbsp;
We have visuals of the 22-yard pitch being covered by a blue covers. And now we await the rain to relent so that the match can begin. The weather in Dharamsala is looking grim and cloudy.&nbsp;&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: RAIN DELAYS TOSS!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>The toss at Dharamsala for the game between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals has been delayed due to rain!&nbsp;</p>
<p>We have visuals of the 22-yard pitch being covered by a blue covers. And now we await the rain to relent so that the match can begin. The weather in Dharamsala is looking grim and cloudy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>
<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508184943" data-timeframe="20250508184943"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011772"><div class="'There's a bit of rain in the air,' says Murali Karthik. 'We have had a bit of a delay even to do the pitch report.'\n\nHe adds that the game will be played on pitch 6.&amp;nbsp;\n\n&quot;Last game, it was pitch 4, we are on pitch no. 6 but it looks very similar. Dimensions - 61m and 68m square boundaries, 75m down the ground. When we have a look at the surface, it is dry, slightly more cracks, it's got that very abrasive nature to it. Last match here, it did turn a little bit more in the second innings but it's a big-scoring ground. Expect lots of runs. Punjab got 236 the other night and then 199 in defence. Delhi have world-class spinners, it might be worth setting (a target) and then spin will come into play,&quot; he says.&amp;nbsp;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
							<div class="ieo-datetime">
								<span>18:49 (IST)</span><span>08 May 2025</span></div>
							<div class="lvblg-sharebx">
