								<a href="#" aria-label=Whatsapp class="sprite-img ieowa" rel="nofollow, noopener" target="_blank"></a>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemprop="liveBlogUpdate" itemscope= "itemscope" >
						<div>
							<time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2025-05-08T18:49:43+05:30"></time>
							<time itemprop="url" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/#tie-lb-20250508184943"></time>
							<span itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="author" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
								<meta content="amitkamath" itemprop="name">
							</span>
							<span itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="image">
								<meta itemprop="url" content="https://images.indianexpress.com/2025/05/PBKS-VS-DC-EVACUATION.jpg">
								<meta content="480" itemprop="width">
								<meta content="267" itemprop="height">
							</span>
							<span itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="publisher">
								<span itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" itemscope="itemscope" itemprop="logo">
									<meta content="https://images.indianexpress.com/2019/11/ienewlogo3_new.png" itemprop="url">
									<meta content="125" itemprop="width">
									<meta content="26" itemprop="height">
								</span>
								<meta content="The Indian Express" itemprop="name">
							</span>
							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T18:51:18+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Weather in Dharamsala">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="'There's a bit of rain in the air,' says Murali Karthik. 'We have had a bit of a delay even to do the pitch report.'

He adds that the game will be played on pitch 6.&nbsp;

"Last game, it was pitch 4, we are on pitch no. 6 but it looks very similar. Dimensions - 61m and 68m square boundaries, 75m down the ground. When we have a look at the surface, it is dry, slightly more cracks, it's got that very abrasive nature to it. Last match here, it did turn a little bit more in the second innings but it's a big-scoring ground. Expect lots of runs. Punjab got 236 the other night and then 199 in defence. Delhi have world-class spinners, it might be worth setting (a target) and then spin will come into play," he says.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Weather in Dharamsala</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>'There's a bit of rain in the air,' says Murali Karthik. 'We have had a bit of a delay even to do the pitch report.'</p>

<p>He adds that the game will be played on pitch 6.&nbsp;</p>

<p>"Last game, it was pitch 4, we are on pitch no. 6 but it looks very similar. Dimensions - 61m and 68m square boundaries, 75m down the ground. When we have a look at the surface, it is dry, slightly more cracks, it's got that very abrasive nature to it. Last match here, it did turn a little bit more in the second innings but it's a big-scoring ground. Expect lots of runs. Punjab got 236 the other night and then 199 in defence. Delhi have world-class spinners, it might be worth setting (a target) and then spin will come into play," he says.&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
						<div class="clear"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</div>
<div class="brdr20 lowlighted" id="tie-lb-20250508181454" data-timeframe="20250508181454"><div class="comment-body-live " id="lb-1011771"><div class="Delhi Capitals were jolted by the withdrawal of England batter Harry Brook. In the IPL 2025 mega auction, DC bought the England star for Rs 6.2 crore. But he pulled out of the contract days ahead of the start of the tournament in order to be free and fresh to play for England. While Brook earned a two-season ban for the withdrawal, Delhi spent almost the entirety of the tournament without naming a replacement.&amp;nbsp;\nFinally, on Wednesday, the DC franchise named Sediqullah Atal as a replacement for Harry Brook.\nA statement from the IPL said: &quot;Sediqullah Atal from Afghanistan has scored 1507 T20 runs in 49 matches. The left-handed batter made his T20I Debut in 2023 and has represented Afghanistan in all three formats. He will now join DC for his base price of Rs 1.25 crore.&quot;" id="lbcontentbody"></div><div class="lvblg-box-shr">
							<div class="ieo-datetime">
								<span>18:14 (IST)</span><span>08 May 2025</span></div>
