							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T18:14:54+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Delhi Capitals bring in Sediqullah Atal">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Delhi Capitals were jolted by the withdrawal of England batter Harry Brook. In the IPL 2025 mega auction, DC bought the England star for Rs 6.2 crore. But he pulled out of the contract days ahead of the start of the tournament in order to be free and fresh to play for England. While Brook earned a two-season ban for the withdrawal, Delhi spent almost the entirety of the tournament without naming a replacement.&nbsp;
Finally, on Wednesday, the DC franchise named Sediqullah Atal as a replacement for Harry Brook.
A statement from the IPL said: "Sediqullah Atal from Afghanistan has scored 1507 T20 runs in 49 matches. The left-handed batter made his T20I Debut in 2023 and has represented Afghanistan in all three formats. He will now join DC for his base price of Rs 1.25 crore."">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Delhi Capitals bring in Sediqullah Atal</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Delhi Capitals were jolted by the withdrawal of England batter Harry Brook. In the IPL 2025 mega auction, DC bought the England star for Rs 6.2 crore. But he pulled out of the contract days ahead of the start of the tournament in order to be free and fresh to play for England. While Brook earned a two-season ban for the withdrawal, Delhi spent almost the entirety of the tournament without naming a replacement.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Finally, on Wednesday, the DC franchise named Sediqullah Atal as a replacement for Harry Brook.</p>
<p>A statement from the IPL said: "Sediqullah Atal from Afghanistan has scored 1507 T20 runs in 49 matches. The left-handed batter made his T20I Debut in 2023 and has represented Afghanistan in all three formats. He will now join DC for his base price of Rs 1.25 crore."</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
