							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T17:26:59+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Why Punjab's 37-run win in previous game was important">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="In their last IPL 2025 game, Punjab Kings took down Lucknow Super Giants by 37 runs at the Himachal Pradesh Cricket Association Stadium in Dharamshala. That win could have significant ramifications on the playoffs, as former India cricketer Anil Kumble had explained right after that match.&nbsp;
"One of those teams could go through on net run rate. So just having an extra point doesn&rsquo;t guarantee anything&mdash;you can&rsquo;t afford to ignore net run rate. That&rsquo;s why Punjab&rsquo;s 37-run win was important. It&rsquo;s still wide open,&rdquo; Kumble had said on JioHotstar.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Why Punjab's 37-run win in previous game was important</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>In their last IPL 2025 game, Punjab Kings took down Lucknow Super Giants by 37 runs at the Himachal Pradesh Cricket Association Stadium in Dharamshala. That win could have significant ramifications on the playoffs, as former India cricketer Anil Kumble had explained right after that match.&nbsp;</p>
<p>"One of those teams could go through on net run rate. So just having an extra point doesn&rsquo;t guarantee anything&mdash;you can&rsquo;t afford to ignore net run rate. That&rsquo;s why Punjab&rsquo;s 37-run win was important. It&rsquo;s still wide open,&rdquo; Kumble had said on JioHotstar.&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
						</div></div>
