							<meta itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" content="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/dc-vs-pbks-ipl-2025-live-cricket-score-playing-11-punjab-kings-delhi-capitals-today-match-updates-9989423/">
							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T16:23:08+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Race to playoffs heats up">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Both Delhi Capitals and Punjab Kings come into this clash with playoffs on their mind, and in their sights.
Punjab, under new captain Shreyas Iyer, have a slightly easier task at hand this season, since they have 15 points from 11 games while Delhi have 13 from the same amount of games.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Race to playoffs heats up</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Both Delhi Capitals and Punjab Kings come into this clash with playoffs on their mind, and in their sights.</p>
<p>Punjab, under new captain Shreyas Iyer, have a slightly easier task at hand this season, since they have 15 points from 11 games while Delhi have 13 from the same amount of games.&nbsp;</p></div>
