							<meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2025-05-08T10:40:25+05:30">
							<meta itemprop="headline" content="ICYMI: Rohit Sharma retires from Test cricket">
							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="India captain Rohit Sharma announced his retirement from Test cricket with immediate effect on Wednesday. This comes a day after the national selectors met and decided to remove him as skipper and go with a new leader for the tour of England that starts next month.
Rohit had already retired from T20 Internationals after leading India to the World Cup title last year. He will, however, continue to play ODIs.

&ldquo;Hello, everyone. I would just like to share that I am retiring from Test cricket. It&rsquo;s been an absolute honour to represent my country in whites,&rdquo; Rohit posted on social media. &ldquo;Thank you for all the love and support over the years. I will continue to represent India in the ODI format.&rdquo;
READ MORE
">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>ICYMI: Rohit Sharma retires from Test cricket</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>India captain Rohit Sharma announced his retirement from Test cricket with immediate effect on Wednesday. This comes a day after the national selectors met and decided to remove him as skipper and go with a new leader for the tour of England that starts next month.</p>
<p class="no_first_intro_para">Rohit had already retired from T20 Internationals after leading India to the World Cup title last year. He will, however, continue to play ODIs.</p>
<div class="ev-meter-content ie-premium-content-block">
<p>&ldquo;Hello, everyone. I would just like to share that I am retiring from Test cricket. It&rsquo;s been an absolute honour to represent my country in whites,&rdquo; Rohit posted on social media. &ldquo;Thank you for all the love and support over the years. I will continue to represent India in the ODI format.&rdquo;</p>
<p><a href="https://indianexpress.com/article/sports/cricket/express-exclusive-selectors-remove-rohit-sharma-test-captaincy-9988779/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>READ MORE</strong></a></p>
</div></div>
