							<meta itemprop="articleBody" content="Hello and welcome to the live coverage of the Indian Premier League 2025 Match No. 58 played between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals at the HPCA Stadium in Dharamsala on Thursday. Stay tuned as we bring you all the live updates of this clash.&nbsp;">
							<div class="lvblg-box">
								<div class="heading-lvblg"><h2>PBKS vs DC LIVE Score, IPL 2025: Hola!</h2></div><div class="body-lvblg"><p>Hello and welcome to the live coverage of the Indian Premier League 2025 Match No. 58 played between Punjab Kings and Delhi Capitals at the HPCA Stadium in Dharamsala on Thursday. Stay tuned as we bring you all the live updates of this clash.&nbsp;</p></div>
							</div>
